1142
01:12:30,720 --> 01:12:35,160
So that nested invocations
have different epsilon tags.

1143
01:12:35,160 --> 01:12:38,040
And so their tangents don't collide.

1144
01:12:38,040 --> 01:12:41,320
That's critical to
