1154
01:13:14,720 --> 01:13:17,200
The phrase higher-order
automatic differentiation

1155
01:13:17,200 --> 01:13:19,560
is used in a bunch of different
senses in the literature.

1156
01:13:19,560 --> 01:13:22,720
When we use it here
